          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-03-18 15:31:36" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>the universe, perhaps with some associated meaning of ‘eon’ or ‘age’ in the sense of the transitory nature of the universe (but this is doubtful in the contexts of {S:05800100200038} and {S:05801100300010})</DefinitionShort>
